
NFS perms on share:
syno ip
read/write
no mapping
sys
tick: enable async + allow users to access mounted subfolders

On PBS shell:

echo "IP:/volume1/BACKUP/Proxmox/PBS /mnt/synology nfs vers=3,nouser,atime,auto,retrans=2,rw,dev,exec 0 0" >> /etc/fstab

mkdir /mnt/synology
mount -a
systemctl daemon-reload
chmod 775 /mnt/synology

create datastore on PBS
name: Synology
Backing Path: /mnt/synology
